title: Buckethead & Travis Dickerson - Chicken Noodles II [2007/FLAC]
description:
[i]Chicken Noodles II[/i] is a collaborative album by Buckethead and Travis Dickerson, and is the follow-up to 2006&#039;s [i]Chicken Noodles[/i] album. It features Buckethead on guitar and Travis Dickerson on keyboards, and was released on the 15th of December through [url="http://travisdickersonmusic.com"]tdrsmusic.com[/url]. More just Guitar and Fender Rhodes Piano. This time, more noodles, more chunks and bits.
